metadata.name: Seagulls on shore
metadata.description:
1/1 unique special NFT that have been released as excluisive edition  - Seagulls on shore

The first work in this collection is about seagulls. My daughter took a picture and I loved these graceful and fast seagulls so much.

Looking at them, you can't even imagine how many wonders, beautiful sea animals, islands, ships and beautiful places they have seen in their lifetime.

And where their last harbor was before they came to our island.

And how beautiful they are in flight!
